\b
\li4 
\v 41 Nnwontofo…î:
\tr 
\tc1 ¬Ý¬Ý Asaf\f + \fr 2.41 \ft Na Asaf y…õ Lewifo…î no mu baako a Dawid yii no maa …îhw…õ…õ nnwomkyer…õ so.\f* abusuafo…î
\tcr2 128
